Here is a simple plist for plex media server to keep it up and running on osx.

After you copy the plist to /Library/LaunchDaemons open terminal then enter these commands:

sudo su
cd /Library/LaunchDaemons
chown root:wheel com.plex.pms.plist
chmod 644 com.plex.pms.plist
launchctl load com.plex.pms.plist
launchctl start com.plex.pms
